Package statdoc.tasks.stata

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    SmclFileTask
    A task to read in Smcl files (stata proprietary log format).
    StataAnalyseDtaFileTask
    Task to process a Stata data file and gather information about its content.
    StataDoFileTask
    Task to parse a do file.
    StataRunDoFileTask
    Task to (auto) run a do file This task should should run a do file if it contains the @statdocrun annotation.
    StataUtils
    general utils to deal with Stata in particular this class allows to convert smcl into various formats like txt and html.
